errors.name: ClosePositionErr
errors.msg: Remove liquitity, collect fees owed and reward then you can close position account

errors.name: ZeroMintAmount
errors.msg: Minting amount should be greater than 0

errors.name: TickInvalidOrder
errors.msg: The lower tick must be below the upper tick

errors.name: TickLowerOverflow
errors.msg: The tick must be greater, or equal to the minimum tick(-443636)

errors.name: TickUpperOverflow
errors.msg: The tick must be lesser than, or equal to the maximum tick(443636)

errors.name: LiquiditySubValueErr
errors.msg: Liquidity sub delta L must be smaller than before

errors.name: LiquidityAddValueErr
errors.msg: Liquidity add delta L must be greater, or equal to before

errors.name: ForbidBothZeroForSupplyLiquidity
errors.msg: Both token amount must not be zero while supply liquidity

errors.name: ZeroAmountSpecified
errors.msg: Swap special amount can not be zero

errors.name: TooSmallInputOrOutputAmount
errors.msg: Swap input or output amount is too small

errors.name: FullRewardInfo
errors.msg: The init reward token reach to the max

errors.name: RewardTokenAlreadyInUse
errors.msg: The init reward token already in use

errors.name: ExceptRewardMint
errors.msg: The reward tokens must contain one of pool vault mint except the last reward

errors.name: InvalidRewardInputAccountNumber
errors.msg: Invalid collect reward input account number

errors.name: NotApproveUpdateRewardEmissiones
errors.msg: Modification of emissiones is allowed within 72 hours from the end of the previous cycle

docs: The current tick of the pool, i.e. according to the last tick transition that was run.

docs: Bitwise representation of the state of the pool
bit0, 1: disable open position and increase liquidity, 0: normal
bit1, 1: disable decrease liquidity, 0: normal
bit2, 1: disable collect fee, 0: normal
bit3, 1: disable collect reward, 0: normal
bit4, 1: disable swap, 0: normal
